  <!-- MP4 FORMAT -->
  <section class="section-seo-block bg-alt" id="instagram-to-mp4" aria-labelledby="mp4-video-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="seo-block-inner" aria-labelledby="mp4-video-heading">
        <div class="seo-block-text">
          <h2 id="mp4-video-heading">Instagram to MP4 — Save Your Videos</h2>
          <p>Every Instagram video saved through DownReels comes as MP4 — the most widely supported format on the planet. Saving Instagram to MP4 takes seconds: paste the link, click download, and the file lands on your device ready to play anywhere. The original resolution and audio are preserved — nothing compressed by DownReels. MP4 works natively on every iPhone, Android phone, Windows PC, Mac, smart TV, and media player without any conversion step required on your end.</p>
          <p>The MP4 file you receive works straight away on any device — phone, tablet, laptop, or smart TV. You can keep it as a personal offline copy, or open it in any media player. No conversion step is needed because MP4 is the native format every modern device already understands.</p>
          <p>Instagram video posts support resolutions up to 1080p Full HD with H.264 encoding and AAC audio. MP4 is natively supported on over 99% of devices, including every iPhone model since 2010, all Android phones, Windows, macOS, and all major smart TVs.</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="seo-block-badge" aria-label="MP4 format highlights">
          <li class="quality-pill"><span class="qp-label">Format</span><span class="qp-value">MP4</span></li>
          <li class="quality-pill"><span class="qp-label">Max Quality</span><span class="qp-value">Source quality</span></li>
          <li class="quality-pill"><span class="qp-label">Conversion</span><span class="qp-value">None needed</span></li>
          <li class="quality-pill"><span class="qp-label">Audio</span><span class="qp-value">Included</span></li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- SAFE & PRIVATE -->
  <section class="section-about" id="safe-and-private-video-downloader" aria-labelledby="safe-video-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="about-inner" aria-labelledby="safe-video-heading">
        <h2 id="safe-video-heading">Safe &amp; Private</h2>
        <p>DownReels works without ever touching your Instagram account. No login is requested at any point — the only thing you share with us is a public post link, and that is used solely to process your request.</p>
        <ul role="list" style="margin-top:16px;padding-left:0;list-style:none;display:grid;gap:10px;">
          <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E1306C" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span>No sign-up, no form, no email address — open the page and the tool is ready immediately</span></li>
          <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E1306C" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span>No personal data collected — we do not ask for your name, email, or any account details</span></li>
          <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E1306C" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span>No payment details ever — free means free, no card required at any step</span></li>
          <li style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E1306C" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span>Protected by HTTPS — the connection between your browser and this page is always encrypted</span></li>
        </ul>
